creator: La Vanguardia Ediciones SL
descriptionHtml:
Take advantage of updated information and a quick and easy navigation. Move your finger across the screen to change section and news. This application identifies which device is running to give the best possible experience once inside.

LaVanguardia.com is the online edition of La Vanguardia newspaper, based in Barcelona, Spain.

This tool offers the following features:

- Access to news from all sections of LaVanguardia.com.
- Read the best articles of Opinion and La Contra sections.
- View all videos posted on our website.
- Give your opinion commenting on the news.
- Send messages, photos and videos directly to the newsroom.
- Share the news on social networks and by email.
- Listen to live radio stations RAC1 and RAC105 while viewing information.

title: La Vanguardia

creator: La Vanguardia Ediciones SL
descriptionHtml:
La Vanguardia offers high quality, rigorous and truthful journalism. Respecting all points of view. Plurality is the hallmark of a newspaper with almost 140 years of history.

La Vanguardia is the leading medium in the Spanish market with more than 23 million monthly readers in Spain alone and more than 50 million around the world.

What can I do with the La Vanguardia app?

- Receive alerts with the last hour to be the first to be informed of the news. In addition to being able to receive alerts when your favorite editor publishes a new article

- Access to all the international and national information minute by minute and to great analyzes of our famous network of international correspondents

- Enjoy mythical sections such as La Contra, redesigned to make the reading experience more satisfactory

- Manage and customize which alerts you want to receive

- Enjoy the video analysis of our editors as well as the highest quality videos

- Access the Opinion module, and enjoy a wide variety of points of view on reality.

- Comment on the news and read the opinions of our community in the articles

- Enjoy the thousands of offers and discounts that the Vanguardia Club provides you in restaurants, movies and tickets of all kinds.

- Access to the paper newspaper in digital version

- Save the news to read later, only for subscribers

- Access to the most V + section with the content most read by our subscribers

- Exclusive access for subscribers to podcasts, hobbies and audio reading of all the news

This application processes personal data, such as your browsing data. If you use this application, we and other selected companies may install cookies or access non-sensitive information on your device in order to create profiles, personalize content, serve ads tailored to your preferences and compile statistics. The use of the application implies that you accept the processing of your personal data.

For more information about the treatments we carry out, you can consult our Privacy Policy at:
https://www.lavanguardia.com/politica-privacidad-app?facet=app

You can also check the conditions of use at:
https://www.lavanguardia.com/aviso-legal-app?facet=app
descriptionShort: Enjoy the latest news from Catalonia, Spain and the world

• Access to the paper newspaper in digital version
• Save the news to read later, only for subscribers
• New section the most V + with direct access to the content most read by subscribers
• Exclusive access to subscribers to podcasts, hobbies and audio reading of all the news

La Vanguardia offers high quality, rigorous and truthful journalism. Respecting all points of view. Plurality is the hallmark of a newspaper with almost 140 years of history.

La Vanguardia is the leading medium in the Spanish market with more than 23 million monthly readers in Spain alone and more than 50 million around the world.

What can I do with the La Vanguardia app?

- Receive alerts with the last hour to be the first to be informed of the news. In addition to being able to receive alerts when your favorite editor publishes a new article

- Access to all the international and national information minute by minute and to great analyzes of our famous network of international correspondents

- Enjoy mythical sections such as La Contra, redesigned to make the reading experience more satisfactory

- Manage and customize which alerts you want to receive

- Enjoy the video analysis of our editors as well as the highest quality videos

- Access the Opinion module, and enjoy a wide variety of points of view on reality.

- Comment on the news and read the opinions of our community in the articles

- Enjoy the thousands of offers and discounts that the Vanguardia Club provides you in restaurants, movies and tickets of all kinds.

- Access to the paper newspaper in digital version

- Save the news to read later, only for subscribers

- Access to the most V + section with the content most read by our subscribers

- Exclusive access for subscribers to podcasts, hobbies and audio reading of all the news

This application processes personal data, such as your browsing data. If you use this application, we and other selected companies may install cookies or access non-sensitive information on your device in order to create profiles, personalize content, serve ads tailored to your preferences and compile statistics. The use of the application implies that you accept the processing of your personal data.

For more information about the treatments we carry out, you can consult our Privacy Policy at:
https://www.lavanguardia.com/politica-privacidad-app?facet=app

You can also check the conditions of use at:
https://www.lavanguardia.com/aviso-legal-app?facet=app
